Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.54,0:00:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Greece, 1965
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.25,0:04:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Jacques, come quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.92,0:04:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- lt's shining!\N- Quick, Jacques! lt's shining in the harbour!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.79,0:04:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.00,0:05:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There! You see it, Jacques?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.13,0:05:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,lt's a coin.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.08,0:05:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- lt's mine! l saw it first!\N- No, you liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.25,0:05:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,- Liar! Liar!\N- We'll see who's lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.67,0:05:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, l'll get it, but no fighting. All right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.38,0:05:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- We'll split it.\N- You can't split a coin. lt's stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.63,0:05:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,- lt's mine! l saw it!\N- He's right! You're stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.88,0:05:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we'll buy something and split that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.17,0:06:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,- Can you stop pointing? l've seen it.\N- l've seen it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.92,0:06:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if it isn't the little Frenchman!\NHow is the little Frenchman?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.00,0:06:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.58,0:06:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't mind if l go instead, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.46,0:06:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,lf you did mind, you'd tell me, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.71,0:06:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.58,0:06:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.54,0:06:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Count!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.83,0:07:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Whose is it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.08,0:07:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You saw it, but l dove for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.46,0:07:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- Roberto, how long?\N- Six!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.50,0:07:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,l throw it back into the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.67,0:07:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You dive, and if you do less than six,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.29,0:07:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,it's yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.71,0:08:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Enzo, l saw the coin first.\NWe'll split it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.50,0:08:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't split a coin, stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.25,0:08:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,ls it... a coin shining there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.08,0:08:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,lt is. lt's a coin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.79,0:08:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,l'll get it for you, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.04,0:08:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,lt will be for the poor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.50,0:08:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.46,0:09:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Time to get up, Jacques.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.83,0:10:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.46,0:11:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't dive every day, Papa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.75,0:11:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you shouldn't eat every day, Jacques.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.25,0:11:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. When l am tired,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.83,0:11:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,the mermaids help me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.79,0:12:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, have you ever seen a mermaid?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.42,0:12:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,l've seen them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.42,0:12:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you want to know where?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.50,0:12:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you ask me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.63,0:12:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,- What?\N- Where l saw mermaids.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.83,0:12:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you ever ask any questions?\Nl always ask the questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.92,0:13:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we are, like two stones,\Nand now l'm talking to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.58,0:13:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ask me something, goddamn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.46,0:13:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did my mother leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.17,0:13:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Pump.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.08,0:13:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mother didn't leave.\NShe went back to America, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.00,0:13:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,lt's her home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.17,0:13:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Women are like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.71,0:13:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Unpredictable.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.92,0:13:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Like the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.33,0:13:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Jacques! The water! Water!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.00,0:13:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Help! l can't breathe!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.08,0:13:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.42,0:13:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Daddy? Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.67,0:14:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Stay here, Jacques!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.50,0:16:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! How did it happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.33,0:16:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, uh... the company asked me to\Nextract everything l could from the wreck.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.13,0:16:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And so the... the divers\Nwere trying to get at the engine...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.17,0:16:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and the boat just turned over\Nin the current!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.29,0:16:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, l... l fucked up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.88,0:16:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.38,0:16:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you help?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.33,0:16:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,How many are down there?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.50,0:16:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,There's just one. We're feeding him lots of air\Nbut... he's not breathing properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.04,0:16:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You've gotta get him outta there, fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.50,0:17:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten thousand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.13,0:17:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Lire?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.83,0:17:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.79,0:17:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.00,0:17:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys aren't gonna try to\Nhold me up at a time like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.54,0:17:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, you tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.58,0:17:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,How much would you say\Na man's life is worth?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.38,0:17:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,ln my village we have a saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.29,0:17:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,How does it go again?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.46,0:17:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,l don't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.58,0:17:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- What's that supposed to mean?\N- Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.67,0:18:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Enzo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.42,0:18:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Forza!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.38,0:18:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Since we have a little time,\Nyou write that cheque?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.92,0:19:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,How much longer can he do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.08,0:19:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,My brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.33,0:19:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,is a world champion.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.79,0:19:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.67,0:21:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Bravo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.79,0:21:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Bravo! Bravo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.83,0:21:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks! Bravo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.58,0:21:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.50,0:21:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.63,0:21:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute! Wait! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.08,0:21:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, thanks, you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.54,0:21:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Really. l mean it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.71,0:21:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.17,0:22:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten thousand dollars, Roberto!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.33,0:22:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you gonna do with the money?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.33,0:22:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Have the car painted.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.50,0:22:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But Giuseppe will do that for 25 dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.29,0:22:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Then tell him to wax it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.13,0:23:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,- What are you really gonna get?\N- A rosary for Mamma...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.38,0:23:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,...a dress for Angelica...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.13,0:23:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,...and a suit that fits you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.00,0:23:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But most important...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.21,0:23:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.96,0:23:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Find me the Frenchman.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.33,0:23:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Find me Jacques Mayol.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.29,0:25:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you Dr Laurence?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.42,0:25:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,No. l'm the assistant.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.42,0:25:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to Peru.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.88,0:26:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,A drink to warm up?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.04,0:26:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.25,0:26:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,- Tea or whiskey?\N- Both.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.42,0:26:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Did... Did l just see a man\Nin a red suit and goggles?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.75,0:26:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.29,0:26:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The insurance person is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.79,0:26:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,lt's about time.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.83,0:26:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Johana Baker.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.08,0:26:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice trip, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.96,0:27:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,lt's three weeks since the accident.\NWe're getting a little anxious.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.04,0:27:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Franck, get out there. He's ready to go in.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.67,0:27:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.96,0:27:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,First dive, two minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.13,0:27:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Who...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.00,0:27:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.21,0:27:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayol. Jacques Mayol.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.96,0:27:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So those are your experiments?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.13,0:27:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Dumping a guy in a frozen lake?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.29,0:27:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The truck fell into a very deep crevasse.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.00,0:27:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We weren't able to rescue the equipment.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.08,0:27:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,l'll have to talk to the driver.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.13,0:28:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,ln the spring, when he melts.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.71,0:28:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You really send him under the ice?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.00,0:28:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He isn't a slave or a convict\Nor anything, is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.13,0:28:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,My dear, science is a cruel mistress.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.21,0:28:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,- How is he gonna breathe?\N- He isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.63,0:28:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.75,0:28:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the sound of his heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.92,0:28:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you hear the speed\Nat which it's slowing down?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.04,0:28:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,lt's incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.08,0:29:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,He's in the fluoroscope now.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.33,0:29:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to his heartbeat!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.54,0:29:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,l can't believe that!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.71,0:29:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,All the blood is concentrated in his brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.58,0:29:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,lt doesn't even feed his limbs any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.50,0:29:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a phenomenon that's only\Nbeen observed in whales and dolphins.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.08,0:29:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.08,0:29:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is he doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.50,0:29:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,l don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.67,0:31:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't someone take him\Na blanket or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.29,0:31:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- l know you.\N- We just met, a few minutes ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.58,0:31:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- ln the lake?\N- No... ln the hut.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.67,0:31:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it must have been someone\Nwho looked a lot like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.17,0:33:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,lt's a present.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.75,0:33:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you gonna open it?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.50,0:33:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you here for a long time?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.25,0:33:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Where do you live?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.00,0:33:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,ln New York.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.42,0:33:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,lt's been nice meeting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.29,0:34:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice... meeting you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.88,0:34:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,l'll only be five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.46,0:35:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Clown.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.17,0:35:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,lt's a llama.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.17,0:35:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Darjeeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.63,0:36:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,l missed you rascals.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.75,0:37:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Jacques, my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.04,0:37:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.71,0:37:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Enzo?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.67,0:37:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,l leave you swimming\Nand 20 years later you're still in the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.33,0:37:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell are you doing? Training?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.13,0:37:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.92,0:37:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.88,0:37:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Check out the suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.92,0:37:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking good, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.13,0:37:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,- You know l'm the world champion?\N- Yeah, l know.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.58,0:37:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The world championship\Nstarts in ten days in Taormina.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.54,0:37:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Be my guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.75,0:37:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Your ticket.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.92,0:37:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.96,0:37:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Because l'm sure you're dying to beat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.29,0:38:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the best, Enzo.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.00,0:38:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,See you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.13,0:42:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,l... l can't hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.29,0:42:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,l said the snowmobile papers\Nare in the glove compartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.79,0:42:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Get the customs office to send me a copy.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.42,0:42:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't get you new equipment\Nuntil our file is complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.13,0:42:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. You'll have them\Nby the end of the week.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.21,0:42:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Great. You've made me a very happy\Ninsurance person. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.42,0:42:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- All right. Goodbye.\N- Dr. Laurence?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.79,0:42:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.29,0:42:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't happen to know how l can\Nget in touch with that diver of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.71,0:42:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Jacques Mayol?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.96,0:42:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The last l heard he was in Taormina,\Nat the World Diving Championships.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.63,0:42:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,ln Sicily.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.33,0:44:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayol... Mayol... No reservation.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.96,0:44:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- Are you sure?\N- Positive, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.88,0:44:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the Hotel San-Domenico?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.08,0:44:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it has been so for 127 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.67,0:44:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful of that car.\Nlt's a new paintjob. OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.96,0:45:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you finally decided to join us.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.29,0:45:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You did the right thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.63,0:45:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Paolo, the key.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.58,0:45:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You remember my little brother Roberto?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.29,0:45:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hi.\N- Hi, Roberto.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.54,0:45:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,- What room have you got?\N- l haven't got one.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.71,0:45:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have a room? Paolo!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.29,0:45:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What did l just hear? l call you to reserve\Na room for my friend Jacques Mayol...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.63,0:45:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and you treat him like a stranger!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.83,0:45:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,- lt's OK, Enzo. l'll go somewhere else.\N- Not only is he a very special friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.46,0:45:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But he is one of the best divers\Nin the world. And you sling him out!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.38,0:45:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you crazy or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.54,0:45:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Drop it, Enzo. l'll find something.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.13,0:45:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Take mine. l'll take the Countess's suite.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.29,0:45:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,She told me she was leaving\Nfor the cemetery.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.96,0:45:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll be more comfortable there! Ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.71,0:46:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,l'm glad you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.50,0:46:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So, after all these years, you must have\Nlots of questions to ask me. Am l right?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.25,0:46:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sure, lots of questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.17,0:46:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, what are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.50,0:46:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,l don't know how to ask the questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.71,0:46:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you married?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.46,0:46:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Me neither. Because of my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.63,0:46:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a curse, my mother. Tornado.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.83,0:46:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Stubborn as a mule.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.71,0:46:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,l was engaged for a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.79,0:46:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,After, Mamma was so mad,\Nthe pasta was bouncing off the walls!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.29,0:47:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So, not married.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.50,0:47:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.67,0:47:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You play the field, like me.\NA girl in every port, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.17,0:47:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,- After all, we're men!\N- Damn right!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.88,0:47:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what l tell them\Nwhen people say you've turned into a fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.71,0:47:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,People say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.29,0:47:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget it! l was joking!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.38,0:47:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,l'll bet you my watch\Nthat she's in my bed tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.38,0:48:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- You know each other?\N- Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.54,0:48:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,- Enzo Molinari. This is a great pleasure.\N- Johana Baker. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.29,0:48:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,This is... a coincidence! lt's unbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.54,0:48:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like to sit down?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.71,0:48:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- l'm not interrupting anything, am l?\N- No, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.29,0:48:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- You staying at the hotel?\N- lt's full. But they recommended a pensione.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.50,0:48:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,- All of Taormina is full.\N- lt's the Free Diving World Championship.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.67,0:48:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,l am, by the way, world champion.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.71,0:48:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- What are you doing in Sicily?\N- l was doing an insurance claim in Palermo...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.50,0:48:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and decided to take a few days off,\Nsee the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.83,0:48:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no place in the world\Nmore beautiful than Sicily.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.67,0:49:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Spaghetti del mare\Nfor the super-dedicated insurance agent.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.88,0:49:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,As l was saying earlier,\Nl am the world champion free diver.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.33,0:49:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Some people say it's\Nthe most virile sport in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.67,0:49:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,One has to admit that seeing those men...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.21,0:49:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,diving headfirst in that deep blue sea,\Nall muscles contracted...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.08,0:49:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,- Enzo...\N- What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.17,0:49:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- Mamma?\N- Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.54,0:49:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.88,0:49:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll kill me if she catches me\Neating pasta in a restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.92,0:49:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Eat up, quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.25,0:49:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You think l can carry these two bags\Nby myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.25,0:49:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Mamma... Roberto and an elevator.\Nlsn't that enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.58,0:49:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,- What have you had today?\N- Just a small coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.29,0:50:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,l am diving tomorrow. Ah,\Nremember little Jacques? Jacques Mayol?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.75,0:50:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And his friend, Johana.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.38,0:50:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,She is beautiful, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.29,0:50:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Spaghetti del mare!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.96,0:50:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,l'm so hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.67,0:50:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.00,0:51:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.25,0:51:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you're gonna be\Nreally busy these days, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.29,0:51:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,l don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.25,0:51:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.96,0:51:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,l... Because l...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.13,0:51:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,l don't know. l just thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.88,0:51:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You have the competition, interviews.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.54,0:51:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,A competition like this requires\Na great deal of concentration... Doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.33,0:51:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You can put down the bags now.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.79,0:51:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to get ready for the ceremony.\NThe Tahitian is the new world champion.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.38,0:51:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,l'm tired. l don't feel like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.54,0:51:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Roberto, the jacket.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.00,0:52:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- This one?\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.83,0:52:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.04,0:52:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the shoes?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.63,0:52:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Very chic.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.33,0:52:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- You don't have anything else, do you?\N- No.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.50,0:52:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it's very chic. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.88,0:52:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Ladies and gentlemen,\Nyour attention, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.33,0:52:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Andre Bonnet, president of the International\NDiving Championship Committee...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.04,0:52:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,this trophy to the new world champion.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.46,0:53:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,This afternoon, our new champion\Ndescended to the remarkable depth...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:00.58,0:53:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,of 310 feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.38,0:53:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,A one-day hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.96,0:53:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr President, if you please...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.08,0:53:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,A new world record. That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.33,0:53:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,lt gives me something to beat tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.96,0:53:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you ever been to Tahiti?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.00,0:53:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,l'll take you there. We'll live in the sun.\NYou'll cook fresh fish...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.92,0:53:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,and we'll make love\Nunder the coconut trees.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.92,0:53:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait.\NHow about you do the cooking?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.42,0:53:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And you forgot the hula.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.63,0:53:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.67,0:53:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,He looks strange, doesn't he?\NLike a baby who just learned to walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.92,0:53:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,- Have you known him long?\N- For ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.33,0:53:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We used to live on the same island in Greece,\Nwhen we were kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.25,0:54:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- What was he like when he was little?\N- Little.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.25,0:54:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Very little.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.38,0:54:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That is, compared to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.54,0:54:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,- l get it, Enzo. You were a superior child.\N- Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.00,0:54:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Johana?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.25,0:54:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You are so crazy about him,\Nyou don't see the truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.83,0:54:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't think of Jacques as a human being.\NHe is from another world.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.17,0:54:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And just what world are you from, Enzo?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.83,0:54:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,ltalia!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.75,0:54:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, my friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.92,0:54:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,you are all invited for a drink\Naround the swim pool.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.08,0:55:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, at lunch, you asked me\Nif l had any questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.42,0:55:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You finally want to know about women!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.04,0:55:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,- Are they what's most important?\N- No.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.29,0:55:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,lt depends.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.38,0:55:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometime they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.08,0:55:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What exactly do you want to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.04,0:55:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.54,0:55:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything about what?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.92,0:55:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,About everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.79,0:56:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So, between Mamma,\NRoberto and Alfredo,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.50,0:56:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,we yell and scream all day long.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.67,0:56:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Except with Angelica. She just cries.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.21,0:56:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, finally, we all end up kissing.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.00,0:56:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you explain that to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.00,0:56:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Because that's what love is all about.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.58,0:56:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,lt's a pain in the ass,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.75,0:56:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,but it keeps us together.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.42,0:56:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,A large...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.63,0:56:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and beautiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.88,0:56:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,family.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.63,0:57:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We've gotta quit this competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.04,0:57:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.25,0:57:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Cos... if we don't,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.79,0:57:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,l'm gonna beat you.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.88,0:57:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.04,0:57:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- What?\N- He looks me in the eye...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.21,0:57:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,like some fucking goldfish...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:27.38,0:57:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and says... "l'm gonna beat you."
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.88,0:57:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what you guys are here for.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.29,0:57:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha! Listen to her!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.46,0:57:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what he's here for!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.92,0:57:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,He's here to lose!\NThat's what he's here for.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:54.38,0:57:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all, l am unbeatable.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.50,0:58:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Second...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.29,0:58:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- How old are you?\N- Two years younger than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.58,0:58:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,As l said,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.79,0:58:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,second of all, you're too skinny.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:08.25,0:58:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got tiny lungs. l still don't understand\Nhow you can dive without getting sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.75,0:58:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The size of the lungs\Nhas nothing to do with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.75,0:58:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,How long can you hold your breath?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.46,0:58:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Longer than you.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.00,1:00:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Take it easy! Jesus!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.63,1:00:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you mad?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:24.00,1:00:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let me help you with this.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:26.21,1:00:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- Who won?\N- What? The Asshole Award?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.54,1:00:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me tell you, it was a tie.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:30.67,1:00:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Acting like a pair of two-year-olds.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.33,1:00:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You could've died in that pool.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.50,1:00:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop moving. You're rocking the boat.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:46.08,1:00:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Luckily, l was there to save you.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.50,1:00:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,My wallet.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:57.00,1:00:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- lt's here.\N- No, no. l wanna show you.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.92,1:01:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.00,1:01:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.88,1:01:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my family.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:42.63,1:01:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of man...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:45.42,1:01:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,has such a family?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:03.71,1:02:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,lt's OK.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.04,1:02:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,lt's all right.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:10.50,1:03:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,All the medics are looking for you, Enzo.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:13.33,1:03:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,l am meditating! Can't you see?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:15.50,1:03:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Jacques does two hours of yoga\Nbefore going down!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:18.71,1:03:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,l can have a five-minute nap!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.88,1:03:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr Molinari, l am sorry,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.25,1:03:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,but you cannot dive\Nin this state of exhaustion.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:46.46,1:03:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you know about the sea?\NNothing!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:49.00,1:03:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So you just take your tubes\Nand your tin cans away.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:52.75,1:03:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The sea is mine.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:54.92,1:03:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,l know when she is ready for me\Nand when she isn't.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:58.13,1:04:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And today she is ready.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:01.96,1:04:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You dive at your own risk.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.33,1:04:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,One minute!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.04,1:05:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Your trousers are too big for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:56.92,1:05:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are they?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:07.25,1:06:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,- Where is everybody?\N- They're gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:11.17,1:06:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Something's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.58,1:06:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:28.75,1:06:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:30.92,1:06:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,l don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:33.04,1:06:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,l've tried for two days. They won't eat.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.54,1:06:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,They won't perform.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:37.67,1:06:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Since we got a new one.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:44.42,1:06:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,lt's finished for today.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.25,1:06:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a new one.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:50.83,1:06:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you tell it's a female?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:54.92,1:06:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,lt's the way she moves.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:35.79,1:08:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be sad.\Nl only took back what was mine.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:39.21,1:08:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Here. A present.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:41.42,1:08:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonight we're having a little party\Namong ourselves. Eight o'clock in my suite.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:48.75,1:08:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr Roberto, tell your brother\Nto be reasonable.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.13,1:08:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody's waiting for him upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:54.71,1:08:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He can't! He's indisposed!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:57.50,1:08:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we call a doctor?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:59.67,1:09:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no! La Mamma,\Nshe is trying something!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.63,1:09:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr Mayol, help us.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:08.00,1:09:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,He refuses to receive his medal,\Nand everybody's waiting for him.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:14.92,1:09:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- l'll do my best.\N- That's very kind of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:18.83,1:09:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,lt's Jacques!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:22.21,1:09:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,My friend! Come on in!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.42,1:09:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr Molinari,\Nallow me to impress upon you...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:27.29,1:09:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,the importance of your attending\Nthe award ceremony...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:31.00,1:09:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,for the press.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.21,1:09:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,l think my brother told you l was indisposed.\NThat should do it, no?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:37.63,1:09:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,l am allowed to be indisposed, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:40.88,1:09:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So you just go tell the press\Nthat the big Enzo Molinari,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:44.83,1:09:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,overwhelmed by his inspiring descent\Nof 324 feet,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:49.79,1:09:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,will not be able to receive his trinket...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:52.67,1:09:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,because he is...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:54.42,1:09:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hm?\N-.. he is...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:56.67,1:09:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Indisposed!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.17,1:10:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Jacques, my friend!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:05.33,1:10:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,- Why don't you pick up your medal?\N- Because pasta should be eaten al dente!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:28.33,1:10:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me know how you find it.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:59.96,1:11:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,My office in New York.\Nlt's really busy back there.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:03.54,1:11:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,l have so much work to do.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:09.17,1:11:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- Do you want some?\N- Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:34.46,1:11:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:37.75,1:11:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,l have to ask you a favour.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:49.67,1:11:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, we're not stealing a dolphin, eh?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:52.08,1:11:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No. l told you, we're just helping one out.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.08,1:11:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Trying to help one out?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:01.33,1:12:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:18.83,1:12:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Taormina by night!\NLucky dolphin, eh?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:25.29,1:12:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Stairs!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:14.08,1:13:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You can stop that now.\NShe has all the water she needs.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:22.79,1:13:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, we did it!\NLet's go back to the party.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:46.75,1:13:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Five minutes, that's all! OK?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:06.58,1:14:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Night.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:08.79,1:14:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- Good night, Jacques.\N- Good night.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:17.63,1:14:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need a stretcher\Nto take her with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:20.63,1:14:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,- You know that?\N- What?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:24.42,1:14:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Dolphins aren't the only ones\Nwho don't feel very good sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:30.58,1:14:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Jacques!\NCan l watch you dive tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:49.58,1:14:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You really do have\Na few things to learn about women.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:26.25,1:15:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What do those guys do?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:28.71,1:15:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,They are paramedics.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:30.88,1:15:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,They wait at 200 feet.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:51.67,1:15:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And him?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:53.63,1:15:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the diver who goes below 300 feet.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:56.71,1:16:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He dives with a helium-oxygen mixture.\NCompressed air is too dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:10.08,1:17:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Three minutes!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:48.92,1:23:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He went down to 360 feet!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:54.00,1:23:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations, Jacques.\Nlt's wonderful. l'm happy for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:58.38,1:24:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:02.04,1:24:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- What is it?\N- Little presents. Nothing much.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:06.21,1:24:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,l knew it. l just knew it.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:14.21,1:24:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you still collect them?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:16.96,1:24:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have that one, do you?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:22.54,1:24:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,lt's beautiful. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:24.96,1:24:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,lt's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:27.17,1:24:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,l knew it. l told Roberto.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:29.33,1:24:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,He's very good, that little Frenchman.\NVery good.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:32.92,1:24:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,ls this a poem?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:34.63,1:24:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's a recipe\Nfor spaghetti frutti del mare.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:41.29,1:24:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,l was right in getting you out here.\NYou're a world champion, my friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:57.83,1:24:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,lt's a measuring tape.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:03.33,1:25:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You see? This is your record.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:05.67,1:25:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Three feet more than mine.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:09.50,1:25:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking at it from here,\Nit doesn't look like much, does it?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:16.92,1:25:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep your little measuring tape, my friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:20.25,1:25:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,lt will be a nice souvenir\Nwhen l beat you next.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:38.17,1:30:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you have a nice night?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:40.92,1:30:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:46.25,1:30:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,l was with the dolphin.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:49.79,1:30:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,All night?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:52.33,1:30:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:54.79,1:30:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,- With the dolphin?\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:04.08,1:31:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,l gotta get back to New York.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:12.29,1:31:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Because l have my job,\Nl have my work and my... life.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:32.21,1:31:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you take me to the train station?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:20.75,1:32:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,lf you're ever in New York,\Ngive me a call, OK?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:44.71,1:32:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- Can l come in?\N- No problem. l enjoy talking in my sleep.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:56.29,1:32:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Wake me up at 11.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:24.50,1:33:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you always talkin'? Nobody's\Ninterested in what you're talkin' about.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:29.75,1:33:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So just stop talkin'! Other people\Nhave things to say! Understand?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:34.00,1:33:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop talkin'! lt's bullshit!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:36.50,1:33:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- She's gone?\N- Yes, she's gone!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:41.88,1:33:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, l'm gonna take care of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:44.00,1:33:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,l've got a job, on an oil rig.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:46.38,1:33:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No sweat.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:47.92,1:33:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,l'm taking you along. OK?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:50.13,1:33:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, get your bags packed.\NYou're coming with me.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:55.38,1:33:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You stupid bastard.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:01.92,1:34:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll make a great team, the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:04.88,1:34:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll see.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:07.00,1:34:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,OK?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:30.46,1:35:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,100 feet.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:38.92,1:35:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still thinking about her.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:41.08,1:35:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't think about her any more.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:44.50,1:35:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,There are so many women in the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:47.21,1:35:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Plenty of women everywhere. Right?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:50.75,1:35:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Smoking is absolutely forbidden.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:52.92,1:35:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,lt isn't lit yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:55.58,1:35:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't even\Ncarry cigarettes on board.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:00.21,1:36:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, we're not supposed to piss, either.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:03.21,1:36:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But that doesn't stop you\Nfrom carrying it on board.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:06.96,1:36:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The rules are the rules.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:10.25,1:36:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your name again?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:13.04,1:36:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Noireuter.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:14.75,1:36:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And where did you say you were from?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:19.25,1:36:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Brussels.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:26.00,1:36:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,200
Dialogue: 0,1:36:40.00,1:36:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,l was 17.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:42.79,1:36:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,l loved her so much, l tried to die for her.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:46.46,1:36:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Two years later,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:48.63,1:36:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,l couldn't even remember her name.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:51.83,1:36:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me tell you,\Ntime erases everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:56.50,1:36:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,l don't want to erase anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:09.08,1:37:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,450 feet. End of descent.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:14.33,1:37:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be left here for 50 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:17.42,1:37:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with the voice?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:20.04,1:37:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,lt's nothing.\NMaybe the helium is up too high.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:24.96,1:37:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,- Does the voice come back?\N- For others, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:28.88,1:37:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,For you... Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:34.42,1:37:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Try speaking to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:37.54,1:37:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,l don't find this funny.\NWe were having a serious conversation!
Dialogue: 0,1:37:46.13,1:37:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,lt's OK for the helium.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:49.63,1:37:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, give me your finger.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:53.58,1:37:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,ls that alcohol?\NThat's really forbidden!
Dialogue: 0,1:37:57.00,1:37:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, do you have any other complaints?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:59.92,1:38:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Make a list and we'll stick it\Non the porthole. OK?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:03.46,1:38:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- Suck your finger.\N- Stop kidding around. lt's...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:07.54,1:38:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,lt's dangerous at this pressure - alcohol.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:11.75,1:38:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Enzo, it's very deep down here.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:14.29,1:38:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, suck your finger.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:23.50,1:38:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, you'll be seeing\Nmermaids everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:33.08,1:38:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,A thousand commanders and we get\Nthe Belgian from Alcoholics Anonymous!
Dialogue: 0,1:38:54.25,1:38:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we clear?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:17.46,1:39:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:50.50,1:42:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,lt's Johana.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:53.58,1:42:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:58.71,1:43:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,l got fired.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:01.67,1:43:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,l got this job with Enzo.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:03.83,1:43:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We got fired, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:06.00,1:43:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:10.04,1:43:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,lt's strange.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:19.00,1:43:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk to me some more.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:21.17,1:43:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,lt's hard. l don't know what else to say.\NYou're so far away.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:27.25,1:43:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me a story.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:31.17,1:43:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,A story?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:36.88,1:43:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know how it is...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:39.83,1:43:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know what you're supposed to do\Nto meet a mermaid?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:47.21,1:43:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You go down to the bottom of the sea...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:50.38,1:43:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,where the water isn't even blue any more...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:53.46,1:43:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and the sky is only a memory...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:55.58,1:43:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and you float there, in the silence,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:59.54,1:44:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and you stay there...
Dialogue: 0,1:44:03.13,1:44:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and you decide... that you'll die for them.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:06.13,1:44:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Only then do they start comin' out.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:08.71,1:44:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,They come, and they greet you,\Nand they judge the love you have for them.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:14.33,1:44:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,lf it's sincere,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:17.88,1:44:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,if it's pure,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:21.54,1:44:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,they'll be with you...
Dialogue: 0,1:44:24.63,1:44:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and take you away for ever.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:34.54,1:44:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,l like that story.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:34.92,1:46:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:38.33,1:46:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,l think l love you.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:15.38,1:47:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You live here?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:17.54,1:47:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:35.67,1:47:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,- Who's that?\N- That's my Uncle Louis.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:45.71,1:47:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,l can't get him out of the bathtub.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:04.58,1:48:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Assassin!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:08.00,1:48:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Uncle Louis!\NThis is my friend Johana!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:13.29,1:48:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Johana is visiting me!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:15.46,1:48:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a bit deaf. He's 75.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:17.63,1:48:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,lt's very nice to meet you, Uncle Louis!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:42.33,1:48:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So, where are you from, Henrietta?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:45.67,1:48:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Johana! New York!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:50.00,1:48:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,New York? What kind of name is that?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:52.83,1:48:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,- No, l'm from New York.\N- Oh, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:57.54,1:49:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The best legs are from New York!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:04.54,1:49:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Uncle Louis...
Dialogue: 0,1:49:08.42,1:49:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Johana is my friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:16.08,1:49:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,She's come to... stay with me...
Dialogue: 0,1:49:20.79,1:49:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,for a while.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:22.96,1:49:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. That way l'll see more of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:26.17,1:49:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you gonna stay?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:29.21,1:49:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- Here.\N- Here? ln my apartment?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:34.21,1:49:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,lt's my apartment.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:36.38,1:49:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Liar! Cheat! Torturer!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:39.63,1:49:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Uncle Louis, go back to your bathtub.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:43.79,1:49:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,l'm going to put a lock on the telephone.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:49.38,1:49:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Have some more wine, Uncle Louis.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:54.46,1:49:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Henrietta.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:57.58,1:49:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,l'll change my name.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:16.75,1:50:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,This is, er...
Dialogue: 0,1:50:18.92,1:50:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,my room.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:37.63,1:50:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Enzo phoned. He's coming over next week\Nfor another competition.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:45.46,1:50:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you gonna compete, too?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:48.50,1:50:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:58.83,1:51:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you'll be all right here?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:53.83,1:51:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,lt's not like him to be late.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:56.00,1:51:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course,\Nsometimes he doesn't show up at all.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:59.67,1:52:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Two dollars?!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:01.96,1:52:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't even need to catch the fish!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:05.96,1:52:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,lt died of cancer!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:22.96,1:52:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,- Where did you get that?\N- That? This is not a "that".
Dialogue: 0,1:52:27.08,1:52:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Bonita Mariposa,\Nthe famous Spanish actress,
Dialogue: 0,1:52:30.79,1:52:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,who is going to be very careful\Nwith the varnish...
Dialogue: 0,1:52:35.21,1:52:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,...and who is spending\Na few days with us.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:43.00,1:52:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,- Where is Mamma?\N- You have 8 hours before she gets here.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:51.67,1:52:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,He's really going totally deaf.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:55.83,1:52:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,l'm not as deaf as you are blind!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:59.63,1:53:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You take care of your eyes,\Nand l'll take care of my ears!
Dialogue: 0,1:53:03.88,1:53:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,l'm sorry, Uncle Louis.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:07.96,1:53:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, drink up, my boy!
Dialogue: 0,1:53:20.63,1:53:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, tell me, what century are you in?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:23.58,1:53:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Second.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:33.58,1:53:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:35.75,1:53:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We're listening to some music.\NWith Enzo.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:41.50,1:53:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- This is Dr Laurence.\N- Ah!
Dialogue: 0,1:53:45.67,1:53:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you must be the famous\NEnzo Molinari.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:49.08,1:53:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,ln the flesh! l have that honour.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:57.79,1:54:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,God... l'm getting wrinkles.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:01.17,1:54:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hm. And l'm getting pimples.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:06.46,1:54:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So, are you gonna live here permanently?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:09.08,1:54:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,l don't know.\NThings have happened so fast.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:12.00,1:54:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We haven't even talked about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:15.79,1:54:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You're very much in love. l can tell.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:22.46,1:54:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You have that look.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:25.63,1:54:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The look of a woman who wants a baby.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:31.96,1:54:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,l haven't even thought of having a baby.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:34.54,1:54:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,God, we're just... starting\Nto get to know each other. lt'd be really...
Dialogue: 0,1:54:39.04,1:54:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Do l really?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:41.13,1:54:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, maybe he's not quite ready, but...
Dialogue: 0,1:54:44.58,1:54:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,he's a nice guy, sensitive.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:49.88,1:54:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, l can't have a baby by myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:53.21,1:54:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not? l have a baby.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:55.75,1:54:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,l loved his father.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:57.88,1:55:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not together any more but...
Dialogue: 0,1:55:00.25,1:55:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,l have his baby.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:04.67,1:55:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,At the end, you do it alone anyway.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:27.17,1:55:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Enzo Molinari for classification.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:41.38,1:55:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What was his last time?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:45.21,1:55:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,l don't know, but it was really long.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:57.33,1:56:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, that's not bad.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:06.04,1:57:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Very good, Enzo. Very good.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:21.21,1:57:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So what? Anybody can have a bad day.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:23.83,1:57:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, l've had many,\Nwhen the sea doesn't want you.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:27.38,1:57:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,lt's never the sea.\Nlt's Mamma, Roberto, that stupid actress!
Dialogue: 0,1:57:33.67,1:57:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't break my balls.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:32.21,1:58:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you have a nice day?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:35.38,1:58:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Enzo had a bad day.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:40.38,1:58:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you dive?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:46.96,1:58:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it didn't feel right.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:56.38,1:59:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,lt's a cute baby, eh?\Nl love that baby.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:47.79,2:00:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Let them try.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:28.50,2:02:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,ls he OK?
Dialogue: 0,2:03:03.67,2:03:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What are they doing?
Dialogue: 0,2:03:06.38,2:03:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,l don't know.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:50.25,2:03:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Great time!
Dialogue: 0,2:04:07.33,2:04:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,How was it?
Dialogue: 0,2:04:10.75,2:04:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,lt was dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:12.92,2:04:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,380 feet,
Dialogue: 0,2:04:15.13,2:04:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,four minutes and 50 seconds underwater.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:18.00,2:04:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Great.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:30.46,2:04:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:37.13,2:04:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,My son, bravo!
Dialogue: 0,2:04:43.88,2:04:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Now...
Dialogue: 0,2:04:47.67,2:04:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,l am sure you heard some people suggest\Nit is too dangerous for us to continue.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:53.21,2:04:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Dangerous because\Nwe don't know how to measure...
Dialogue: 0,2:04:56.13,2:04:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,the physiological consequences\Nof this type of dive.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:59.96,2:05:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And also because the scuba divers\Nare not used to going down below 300 feet.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:06.33,2:05:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- But...\N- What's he saying?
Dialogue: 0,2:05:08.50,2:05:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,...we asked the free divers,
Dialogue: 0,2:05:11.13,2:05:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and they all insist...
Dialogue: 0,2:05:13.42,2:05:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,that the competition continue.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:24.13,2:05:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck to you all. Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:41.88,2:06:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,One minute!
Dialogue: 0,2:08:34.13,2:08:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't stay here!
Dialogue: 0,2:09:03.79,2:09:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you see him?
Dialogue: 0,2:09:08.58,2:09:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Do you see him?
Dialogue: 0,2:09:26.58,2:09:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Jacques!
Dialogue: 0,2:10:22.13,2:10:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,400 feet.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:24.04,2:10:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,400 feet!
Dialogue: 0,2:10:43.58,2:10:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You all right?
Dialogue: 0,2:10:55.17,2:10:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,l'll be right there!
Dialogue: 0,2:10:57.25,2:10:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi! Come on in.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:59.21,2:11:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- No. l wanted to say goodbye.\N- You're leaving?
Dialogue: 0,2:11:02.54,2:11:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.\NCould you please give this to Enzo?
Dialogue: 0,2:11:11.54,2:11:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,lt's no use.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:14.63,2:11:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Just tell him l said goodbye,\Nand give him a kiss for me. OK?
Dialogue: 0,2:11:19.88,2:11:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- Promise?\N- Promise.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:24.79,2:11:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you shouldn't give up so easily.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:28.63,2:11:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's a present for you.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:35.17,2:11:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,lt's your baby.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:41.83,2:11:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Believe me, it will change your life,
Dialogue: 0,2:11:44.50,2:11:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,only for the better.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:49.75,2:11:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You take care of yourself, Johana.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:52.92,2:11:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You, too.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:05.88,2:14:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to Greece, Jacques!\NHow are you?
Dialogue: 0,2:14:08.63,2:14:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome, Johana. Have a good trip?
Dialogue: 0,2:14:11.00,2:14:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, let me give you all the information.\NCome with me.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:32.92,2:14:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This is making me sick.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:36.92,2:14:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,2:14:40.58,2:14:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you give me a glass of water?
Dialogue: 0,2:15:04.42,2:15:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Nervous about the competition?
Dialogue: 0,2:15:14.75,2:15:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What's it feel like when you dive?
Dialogue: 0,2:15:23.25,2:15:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,lt's a feeling of slipping without falling.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:28.17,2:15:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The hardest thing is when\Nyou hit the bottom.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:33.75,2:15:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,2:15:39.63,2:15:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you have to find\Na good reason to come back up.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:43.08,2:15:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And l have a hard time finding one.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:53.08,2:15:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we have the same problem.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:58.00,2:15:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,2:15:59.17,2:16:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Because l have a hard time\Nfinding a good reason to stay.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:25.96,2:16:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,l found one.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:44.25,2:16:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,ls he here?
Dialogue: 0,2:16:47.79,2:16:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:51.88,2:16:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:36.83,2:17:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,lt scares me when you look\Nat the sea like that.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:46.33,2:17:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,l used to dive here when l was a boy.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:52.25,2:17:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,l have something\Nl want to talk to you about.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:55.13,2:17:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Not here.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:20.17,2:18:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we talk here?
Dialogue: 0,2:18:42.50,2:18:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's talk about my world.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:47.17,2:18:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,My world is you.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:55.00,2:18:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,l love you.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:59.92,2:19:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,l wanna live with you.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:03.50,2:19:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,l wanna have a baby with you.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:07.33,2:19:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,l wanna have a house with you.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:09.50,2:19:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,A car with you. A dog with you.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:12.79,2:19:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You know?
Dialogue: 0,2:19:14.88,2:19:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Jacques, l think l might be pregnant!
Dialogue: 0,2:19:23.21,2:19:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,2:20:14.75,2:20:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow is going to be a big day.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:45.25,2:21:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,When l analysed the data from\NMayol's last dive, it became apparent.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:49.63,2:21:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,At the depths these men are diving,\Nit is a physiological impossibility...
Dialogue: 0,2:21:53.54,2:21:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,that they could retain enough oxygen\Nto make it to the surface.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:57.38,2:22:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The pressure is so strong, it stops the oxygen\Nfrom circulating through the body.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:03.21,2:22:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,To attempt to break Mayol's record now...
Dialogue: 0,2:22:05.96,2:22:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,is simple suicide.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:10.38,2:22:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,2:22:13.63,2:22:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, l understand.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:16.96,2:22:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Today is just training.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:21.29,2:22:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- Molinari is a 17-time world champion.\N- Three minutes!
Dialogue: 0,2:22:24.63,2:22:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to tell him he can't dive?
Dialogue: 0,2:22:32.50,2:22:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Cancel the competition.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:41.75,2:22:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Two minutes!
Dialogue: 0,2:22:49.33,2:22:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Get Mayol in here.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:57.08,2:22:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,One minute!
Dialogue: 0,2:23:14.58,2:23:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,They wanna cancel the competition.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:17.21,2:23:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,For a while.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:20.46,2:23:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,2:23:23.63,2:23:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,lt's not safe, they say.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:30.13,2:23:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The doctors say...
Dialogue: 0,2:23:33.54,2:23:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,we can't go deeper and survive.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:38.08,2:23:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You say that because you have the title.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:42.25,2:23:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,l would never cheat you.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:47.63,2:23:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That's very nice of you.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:57.50,2:24:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Jesus!\Nl told you to tell him not to go!
Dialogue: 0,2:24:00.58,2:24:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,lt's not my fault! l told him!
Dialogue: 0,2:24:07.63,2:24:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- No, no, no!\N- And then they die!
Dialogue: 0,2:24:09.79,2:24:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,lt's the first time\Nl've organised a competition!
Dialogue: 0,2:25:25.25,2:25:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,2:25:38.42,2:25:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Get away!
Dialogue: 0,2:25:40.17,2:25:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you get away?!
Dialogue: 0,2:25:42.00,2:25:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Goddamn it!
Dialogue: 0,2:25:43.58,2:25:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Get away!
Dialogue: 0,2:25:46.00,2:25:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- Give him some time! Leave him alone!\N- Out!
Dialogue: 0,2:25:52.00,2:25:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Clear off!
Dialogue: 0,2:26:12.83,2:26:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You were right.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:17.88,2:26:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,2:26:20.96,2:26:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,lt's much better down there.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:27.08,2:26:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,lt's a better place.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:45.75,2:26:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Push me back in the water.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:49.58,2:26:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,No, l can't.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:58.38,2:27:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Take me back down.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:08.33,2:27:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:04.38,2:28:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, look!
Dialogue: 0,2:28:50.75,2:28:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,- Up with the arms... Over the top...\N- Come on, Jacques.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:57.58,2:28:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get a heartbeat.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:59.92,2:29:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, breathe!
Dialogue: 0,2:29:01.92,2:29:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Jacques. Come on, Jacques!
Dialogue: 0,2:29:10.29,2:29:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Come back, Jacques!
Dialogue: 0,2:29:36.63,2:29:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Jacques! Stay with us!
Dialogue: 0,2:30:04.13,2:30:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. Good.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:06.33,2:30:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Good boy.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:13.79,2:30:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Very good.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:35.33,2:30:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:41.75,2:30:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Get some sleep.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:04.04,2:31:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll talk later.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:09.13,2:31:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You sleep now.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:22.54,2:31:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,l love you.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:30.88,2:31:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Laurence...\NThis just arrived for you.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:56.75,2:31:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,l wasn't on the boat.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:05.08,2:32:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The only time in 20 years,
Dialogue: 0,2:32:09.92,2:32:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and l wasn't on the boat.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:17.42,2:32:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,l must go now, tell Mamma.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:49.13,2:32:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,l know this isn't a good time for this, but...
Dialogue: 0,2:32:52.42,2:32:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,l have the results of your test here.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:55.92,2:32:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you're pregnant.
Dialogue: 0,2:33:08.75,2:33:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you happy?
Dialogue: 0,2:33:11.83,2:33:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yes.\N- Good.
Dialogue: 0,2:33:14.25,2:33:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,l'm happy.
Dialogue: 0,2:33:18.46,2:33:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,l'm scared,
Dialogue: 0,2:33:20.63,2:33:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,but l'm happy.
Dialogue: 0,2:33:24.04,2:33:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,2:33:25.96,2:33:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,no more ouzo.
Dialogue: 0,2:33:29.50,2:33:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,No more cigarettes.
